messageBody:
Thanks, I fixed the path to inlcude lib path of java directory

"John L. Webber" <John.Webber@...> wrote:Is the path to the jar file correct? If so, are the file permissions
such that the jar file can be read? What java version are you using (try
java -version).

The stack trace you gave usually occurs when the jar file doesn't exist
(or can't be read).

John
